{summary, "A GUI to mnesia and ets"}.
{abstract,
  "This is a Graphical User Interface which make it easy to explore mnesia "
  "and ets tables. "
  "With trex you can read, write and search in mnesia/ets tables, dump the "
  "tables to a file and look at it off-line, log updates to mnesia tables "
  "for debugging purposes, among other things."}.
